OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with occasional,
OL,6,Fmainly light rain, though a few
OL,7,Fheavier bursts are possible in the
OL,8,Fwest. Still a lot of dry weather, and
OL,9,Fthe northwest will become sunnier
OL,10,Flater in the day.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPatchy rain in east clearing
OL,13,Fthis evening with some clear spells
OL,14,Ffor a time tonight. More cloud and
OL,15,Frain will reach the Isles and West
OL,16,FHighland later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
