OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with some rain in the
OL,6,Fwest pushing east and weakening, with
OL,7,Fsome brighter spells developing in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Heavier rain in evening
OL,9,Fwith southerly gales over the Hebrides.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FSunny
OL,12,Fintervals and blustery showers on
OL,13,FWednesday. Heavy rain and gales on
OL,14,FThursday, showery later. Colder with
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers on Friday, snow
OL,16,Fon hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
